name: Booking Consulation Appointment
description: A web application that allows users to book an appointment with a consultant. The user can view the available slots and book an appointment. The consultant can view the appointments and mark them as completed.

name: Personal Portfolio
description: A personal portfolio website that showcases my projects, educations, and skills. The website is built using ReactJS and Material UI.

name: Project Management System
description: A web application that allows users to create projects, add tasks, and assign tasks to team members. The user can view the project details and update the status of the project.
